{"tid":158708,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴打巴士站違泊 警一周發722萬張「牛肉乾」","createTime":"2017-03-16T12:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T12:51:04.000Z","uid":66941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f899927c924d76b2fe6a7826f1aec3aeb639d7f","tid":158708,"uid":66941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:45:31.000Z","msg":"警方昨日完成為期一周的全港反違例泊車及引致交通阻塞的違例執法行動，期間共發出了4.2萬張定額罰款通知書，及拖走30架車輛，其中在巴士站附近發出的定額罰款通知書佔722張。<br />\n　　發言人表示，是次行動特別針對引致交通意外及道路阻塞的不良駕駛行為，旨在改善道路使用者的駕駛態度，以減少交通意外和保持交通暢順。警方會繼續嚴厲執法，於各區打擊非法泊車，並會在不作任何警告下發出定額罰款通知書。發言人呼籲駕駛者顧己及人，注意安全，並尊重其他道路使用者的權利。 <br />\n <br />\n&copy; 由 星島網即時新聞 提供<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/newsinstant/%E5%9A%B4%E6%89%93%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E7%AB%99%E9%81%95%E6%B3%8A-%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E7%99%BC722%E8%90%AC%E5%BC%B5%E3%80%8C%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E4%B9%BE%E3%80%8D/ar-BBybYS3?li=AA570l&amp;ocid=spartandhp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Fnewsinstant%2F%25E5%259A%25B4%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%258A-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2591%25A8%25E7%2599%25BC722%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%2589%259B%25E8%2582%2589%25E4%25B9%25BE%25E3%2580%258D%2Far-BBybYS3%3Fli%3DAA570l%26ocid%3Dspartandhp&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=ae594ebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/newsinstant/%E5%9A%B4%E6%89%93%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E7%AB%99%E9%81%95%E6%B3%8A-%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E7%99%BC722%E8%90%AC%E5%BC%B5%E3%80%8C%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E4%B9%BE%E3%80%8D/ar-BBybYS3?li=AA570l&amp;ocid=spartandhp</a>"},{"pid":"ab458aa6d349080fc43641c094e379e189528145","tid":158708,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:46:20.000Z","msg":"星島up乜9"},{"pid":"caac982e730f68243ff85bdcca9df1bcc6d406db","tid":158708,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T